---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Spirit Media Publishing — Equipping Voices. Amplifying Purpose."
  description="Spirit Media Publishing helps faith-driven authors, speakers, and ministry leaders publish, market, and distribute their message to the world."
>
  <main id="main-content">

    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
         HERO
         ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-navy-950 px-6 py-24 sm:py-32 lg:px-8">
      <!-- Subtle gold gradient accent -->
      <div
        class="pointer-events-none absolute -top-40 left-1/2 h-[600px] w-[600px] -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full bg-gold-500 opacity-5 blur-3xl"
        aria-hidden="true"
      ></div>

      <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
        <p class="font-serif text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-gold-400">
          Spirit Media Publishing
        </p>
        <h1 class="mt-4 font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight tracking-tight text-white sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">
          Equipping Voices.<br />
          <span class="text-gold-400">Amplifying Purpose.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-8 text-navy-200">
          We partner with faith-driven authors, speakers, and ministry leaders to publish, market, and
          distribute messages that transform lives and advance the Kingdom.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 sm:flex-row sm:gap-6">
          <a
            href="/publishing"
            class="rounded-md bg-gold-500 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-navy-950 shadow-sm transition-colors hover:bg-gold-400 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-gold-500"
          >
            Start Publishing
          </a>
          <a
            href="/about"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-navy-100 transition-colors hover:text-white"
          >
            Our mission <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
         MISSION STRIP
         ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <section class="border-y border-gold-200 bg-gold-50 px-6 py-12 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl text-center">
        <p class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold leading-relaxed text-navy-900 sm:text-2xl">
          "We exist to be the hands and feet of the Father — helping His messengers carry the
          message further, louder, and with excellence."
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-navy-500">— Kevin &amp; Shelly, Founders</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
         SERVICES OVERVIEW
         ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <section class="bg-white px-6 py-24 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-gold-500">What We Do</p>
          <h2 class="mt-2 font-serif text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-navy-900 sm:text-4xl">
            Everything your message needs to reach the world
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">
            From manuscript to marketplace — we offer end-to-end publishing and marketing services
            designed specifically for Kingdom voices.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
          {
            [
              {
                icon: '<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6.042A8.967 8.967 0 0 0 6 3.75c-1.052 0-2.062.18-3 .512v14.25A8.987 8.987 0 0 1 6 18c2.305 0 4.408.867 6 2.292m0-14.25a8.966 8.966 0 0 1 6-2.292c1.052 0 2.062.18 3 .512v14.25A8.987 8.987 0 0 0 18 18a8.967 8.967 0 0 0-6 2.292m0-14.25v14.25" />',
                title: 'Book Publishing',
                body: 'Full-service eBook and print publishing — from editing and cover design to ISBN, distribution on Amazon, Kindle, and beyond.',
                href: '/publishing',
              },
              {
                icon: '<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10.34 15.84c-.688-.06-1.386-.09-2.09-.09H7.5a4.5 4.5 0 1 1 0-9h.75c.704 0 1.402-.03 2.09-.09m0 9.18c.253.962.584 1.892.985 2.783.247.55.06 1.21-.463 1.511l-.657.38c-.551.318-1.26.117-1.527-.461a20.845 20.845 0 0 1-1.44-4.282m3.102.069a18.03 18.03 0 0 1-.59-4.59c0-1.586.205-3.124.59-4.59m0 9.18a23.848 23.848 0 0 1 8.835 2.535M10.34 6.66a23.847 23.847 0 0 0 8.835-2.535m0 0A23.74 23.74 0 0 0 18.795 3m.38 1.125a23.91 23.91 0 0 1 1.014 5.395m-1.014 8.855c-.118.38-.245.754-.38 1.125m.38-1.125a23.91 23.91 0 0 0 1.014-5.395m0-3.46c.495.413.811 1.035.811 1.73 0 .695-.316 1.317-.811 1.73m0-3.46a24.347 24.347 0 0 1 0 3.46" />',
                title: 'Marketing Strategy',
                body: 'Multi-layer marketing plans — social media, email funnels, Amazon optimization, press outreach, and paid ads tailored to your audience.',
                href: '/marketing',
              },
              {
                icon: '<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 3v11.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 6 16.5h2.25M3.75 3h-1.5m1.5 0h16.5m0 0h1.5m-1.5 0v11.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 18 16.5h-2.25m-7.5 0h7.5m-7.5 0-1 3m8.5-3 1 3m0 0 .5 1.5m-.5-1.5h-9.5m0 0-.5 1.5m.75-9 3-3 2.148 2.148A12.061 12.061 0 0 1 16.5 7.605" />',
                title: 'Brand Development',
                body: 'Author branding, platform building, and ministry identity design — so your name carries the weight your message deserves.',
                href: '/marketing',
              },
              {
                icon: '<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m15.75 10.5 4.72-4.72a.75.75 0 0 1 1.28.53v11.38a.75.75 0 0 1-1.28.53l-4.72-4.72M4.5 18.75h9a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25-2.25v-9a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-2.25-2.25h-9A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25 7.5v9a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25 2.25Z" />',
                title: 'Media Production',
                body: 'Podcast setup, video content strategy, and multimedia resources that extend your reach beyond the printed page.',
                href: '/media-center',
              },
              {
                icon: '<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 21a9.004 9.004 0 0 0 8.716-6.747M12 21a9.004 9.004 0 0 1-8.716-6.747M12 21c2.485 0 4.5-4.03 4.5-9S14.485 3 12 3m0 18c-2.485 0-4.5-4.03-4.5-9S9.515 3 12 3m0 0a8.997 8.997 0 0 1 7.843 4.582M12 3a8.997 8.997 0 0 0-7.843 4.582m15.686 0A11.953 11.953 0 0 1 12 10.5c-2.998 0-5.74-1.1-7.843-2.918m15.686 0A8.959 8.959 0 0 1 21 12c0 .778-.099 1.533-.284 2.253m0 0A17.919 17.919 0 0 1 12 16.5c-3.162 0-6.133-.815-8.716-2.247m0 0A9.015 9.015 0 0 1 3 12c0-1.605.42-3.113 1.157-4.418" />',
                title: 'Global Distribution',
                body: 'Get your book into readers\' hands worldwide — eBook, print-on-demand, and translation into 100+ languages through our distribution network.',
                href: '/publishing',
              },
              {
                icon: '<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M18 18.72a9.094 9.094 0 0 0 3.741-.479 3 3 0 0 0-4.682-2.72m.94 3.198.001.031c0 .225-.012.447-.037.666A11.944 11.944 0 0 1 12 21c-2.17 0-4.207-.576-5.963-1.584A6.062 6.062 0 0 1 6 18.719m12 0a5.971 5.971 0 0 0-.941-3.197m0 0A5.995 5.995 0 0 0 12 12.75a5.995 5.995 0 0 0-5.058 2.772m0 0a3 3 0 0 0-4.681 2.72 8.986 8.986 0 0 0 3.74.477m.94-3.197a5.971 5.971 0 0 0-.94 3.197M15 6.75a3 3 0 1 1-6 0 3 3 0 0 1 6 0Zm6 3a2.25 2.25 0 1 1-4.5 0 2.25 2.25 0 0 1 4.5 0Zm-13.5 0a2.25 2.25 0 1 1-4.5 0 2.25 2.25 0 0 1 4.5 0Z" />',
                title: 'Community & Coaching',
                body: 'Join the Kingdom Messenger Collective — a thriving community of faith-driven authors and speakers growing together in faith and business.',
                href: '/join',
              },
            ].map(({ icon, title, body, href }) => (
              <div class="group rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 bg-gray-50 p-8 transition-shadow hover:shadow-md">
                <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-navy-50">
                  <svg
                    class="h-6 w-6 text-navy-700"
                    fill="none"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    stroke-width="1.5"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    aria-hidden="true"
                    set:html={icon}
                  />
                </div>
                <h3 class="mt-5 font-serif text-lg font-semibold text-navy-900">{title}</h3>
                <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-gray-600">{body}</p>
                <a
                  href={href}
                  class="mt-4 inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-sm font-medium text-navy-700 transition-colors hover:text-gold-600"
                >
                  Learn more <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
                </a>
              </div>
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
         FEATURED BRANDS / IMPRINTS
         ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <section class="bg-navy-950 px-6 py-24 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-gold-400">Our Brands</p>
          <h2 class="mt-2 font-serif text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl">
            Kingdom-focused imprints &amp; initiatives
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-7 text-navy-300">
            Each brand under Spirit Media Publishing carries a distinct mission to reach a specific
            audience with the Father's heart.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
          {
            [
              {
                href: '/fathers-heart-bible',
                title: "Father's Heart Bible",
                tagline: 'A Bible illuminated by the Father\'s love',
                color: 'border-gold-500',
                accent: 'text-gold-400',
              },
              {
                href: '/kingdom-messenger-collective',
                title: 'Kingdom Messenger Collective',
                tagline: 'Community for faith-driven voices',
                color: 'border-navy-400',
                accent: 'text-navy-300',
              },
              {
                href: '/work-on-yourself',
                title: 'Work on Yourself',
                tagline: 'Personal development rooted in faith',
                color: 'border-gold-500',
                accent: 'text-gold-400',
              },
              {
                href: '/express-books',
                title: 'Express Books',
                tagline: 'Fast-track publishing for busy authors',
                color: 'border-navy-400',
                accent: 'text-navy-300',
              },
            ].map(({ href, title, tagline, color, accent }) => (
              <a
                href={href}
                class:list={[
                  'group rounded-2xl border-t-4 bg-navy-900 p-8 transition-colors hover:bg-navy-800',
                  color,
                ]}
              >
                <h3 class:list={['font-serif text-lg font-semibold leading-snug', accent]}>
                  {title}
                </h3>
                <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-navy-300">{tagline}</p>
                <span class="mt-4 inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-xs font-medium text-navy-400 transition-colors group-hover:text-white">
                  Learn more <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
                </span>
              </a>
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
         WHY SPIRIT MEDIA
         ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <section class="bg-white px-6 py-24 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-16 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:items-center">
          <div>
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-gold-500">
              Why Choose Us
            </p>
            <h2 class="mt-2 font-serif text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-navy-900 sm:text-4xl">
              More than a publisher — a Kingdom partner
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-6 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">
              Most publishing companies treat your book like a product. We treat it like a
              ministry. Every decision we make is filtered through the question: <em>Does this
              advance the Father's purposes?</em>
            </p>

            <dl class="mt-10 space-y-6">
              {
                [
                  {
                    term: 'Faith-Centered Approach',
                    detail:
                      'Our team prays over every project. We believe publishing is a sacred assignment, and we handle it with that reverence.',
                  },
                  {
                    term: 'End-to-End Support',
                    detail:
                      'From your first draft to your launch day — and beyond. We don\'t disappear after the book is published.',
                  },
                  {
                    term: 'Proven Results',
                    detail:
                      'Our authors have reached readers in over 30 countries, hit Amazon bestseller lists, and built thriving ministries and businesses.',
                  },
                  {
                    term: 'Transparent Pricing',
                    detail:
                      'No hidden fees, no surprise upsells. You know exactly what you\'re getting before you sign anything.',
                  },
                ].map(({ term, detail }) => (
                  <div class="flex gap-4">
                    <div class="mt-1 flex h-6 w-6 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-gold-100">
                      <svg
                        class="h-3.5 w-3.5 text-gold-600"
                        viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                        fill="currentColor"
                        aria-hidden="true"
                      >
                        <path
                          fill-rule="evenodd"
                          d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 0 1 .143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 0 1-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 0 1 1.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 0 1 1.05-.143Z"
                          clip-rule="evenodd"
                        />
                      </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                      <dt class="font-semibold text-navy-900">{term}</dt>
                      <dd class="mt-1 text-sm leading-6 text-gray-600">{detail}</dd>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                ))
              }
            </dl>
          </div>

          <!-- Stats panel -->
          <div class="rounded-3xl bg-navy-950 px-8 py-12 text-center">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-8">
              {
                [
                  { stat: '500+', label: 'Authors served' },
                  { stat: '30+', label: 'Countries reached' },
                  { stat: '100+', label: 'Language translations' },
                  { stat: '#1', label: 'Amazon bestsellers' },
                ].map(({ stat, label }) => (
                  <div>
                    <p class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold text-gold-400">{stat}</p>
                    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-navy-300">{label}</p>
                  </div>
                ))
              }
            </div>
            <div class="mt-10 border-t border-navy-800 pt-8">
              <p class="text-sm leading-6 text-navy-300">
                Join hundreds of faith-driven authors who chose Spirit Media Publishing to carry
                their message to the world.
              </p>
              <a
                href="/contact"
                class="mt-6 inline-block rounded-md bg-gold-500 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-navy-950 transition-colors hover:bg-gold-400"
              >
                Request a Free Consultation
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
         TESTIMONIALS
         ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <section class="bg-gray-50 px-6 py-24 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-gold-500">Testimonials</p>
          <h2 class="mt-2 font-serif text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-navy-900 sm:text-4xl">
            What our authors are saying
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 lg:grid-cols-3">
          {
            [
              {
                quote:
                  'Spirit Media Publishing didn\'t just publish my book — they helped me find my voice. The whole team treats you like family.',
                author: 'Pastor James T.',
                role: 'Author, "Arise and Shine"',
              },
              {
                quote:
                  'I was skeptical at first, but from the cover design to the launch strategy, everything exceeded my expectations. My book hit #1 on Amazon in its category.',
                author: 'Dr. Angela R.',
                role: 'Speaker & Author',
              },
              {
                quote:
                  'The marketing plan they built for me was unlike anything I\'d seen. Within 90 days my audience had tripled and I had speaking invitations coming in regularly.',
                author: 'Minister David K.',
                role: 'Author & Ministry Leader',
              },
            ].map(({ quote, author, role }) => (
              <figure class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-8 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-100">
                <blockquote class="text-sm leading-7 text-gray-700">
                  <p>"{quote}"</p>
                </blockquote>
                <figcaption class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-3">
                  <div class="flex h-10 w-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-navy-100 font-serif text-base font-bold text-navy-700">
                    {author[0]}
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-navy-900">{author}</p>
                    <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">{role}</p>
                  </div>
                </figcaption>
              </figure>
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
         JOIN COMMUNITY
         ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <section class="bg-white px-6 py-24 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl">
        <div class="rounded-3xl bg-navy-900 px-8 py-16 text-center sm:px-16">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-gold-400">
            Kingdom Messenger Collective
          </p>
          <h2 class="mt-3 font-serif text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl">
            You don't have to do this alone
          </h2>
          <p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-xl text-base leading-7 text-navy-300">
            Join our growing community of faith-driven authors, speakers, and ministry leaders who
            are building their platforms, publishing their messages, and supporting each other along
            the way.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 sm:flex-row">
            <a
              href="/join"
              class="rounded-md bg-gold-500 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-navy-950 shadow-sm transition-colors hover:bg-gold-400"
            >
              Join the Collective
            </a>
            <a
              href="/about"
              class="text-sm font-semibold text-navy-200 transition-colors hover:text-white"
            >
              Learn about our mission <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
         FINAL CTA BANNER
         ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-gold-500 px-6 py-20 lg:px-8">
      <div
        class="pointer-events-none absolute -right-20 -top-20 h-64 w-64 rounded-full bg-gold-400 opacity-40 blur-3xl"
        aria-hidden="true"
      ></div>
      <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-navy-950 sm:text-4xl">
          Ready to publish your message?
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-7 text-navy-800">
          Let's talk about your vision. Our team will walk you through every option and help you
          find the right path forward — no pressure, no obligation.
        </p>
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="mt-8 inline-block rounded-md bg-navy-950 px-8 py-3.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm transition-colors hover:bg-navy-900 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-navy-900"
        >
          Request a Free Consultation
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</Layout>
